snippet.title: Testament: The Order of High Human (First-Person Metroidvania) - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Developer Fairyship games has announced Testament: The Order of High Human, a new first-person Metroidvania action-adventure/RPG set in a post-apocalyptic fantasy world. It's in development for PC. 

Wishlist it on Steam if you're interested:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/2176430/Testament_The_Order_of_HighHuman/

#TestamentTheOrderofHighHuman #Metroidvania
